<li>[8] <a href="http://www.vatican.va/holy_father/john_paul_ii/speeches/2002/june/documents/hf_jp-ii_spe_20020610_venice-declaration_en.htm" target="_blank">Common declaration on environmental ethics of John Paul II and the Ecumenical Patriarch His Holiness Bartholomew I</a>. Rome – Venice, 10 June 2002. </li>

